metadata.name: WeDream Founders Pass #1
metadata.description: WeDream provides access for everyone to create, connect, and share in Augmented Reality. The WeDream Founders Pass Collection consists of 1,000 unique digital art pieces which will be released in batches. Be among one of the first people to test new features in our augmented reality social platform, receive unique item drops, and participate in the success of the WeDream platform as the company grows!
